Source.Name: python-pygithub
Source.Summary: Typed interactions with the GitHub API
Source.Description: PyGitHub is a Python library to access the GitHub API and Github Enterprise API. This library enables you to manage GitHub resources such as repositories, user profiles, and organizations in your Python applications.
